    "description": {
      "value": "<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&gt;@Compendium[sfrpg.rules.Conditions]</p>\n<hr/>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">You move at half speed, you can’t run or charge, and you take a –3 penalty to your Armor Class, attack rolls, melee damage rolls, thrown weapon damage rolls, Reflex saving throws, initiative checks, and Strength- and Dexterity-based skill and ability checks.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The amount of bulk you can carry without becoming encumbered is reduced by 3.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">After 1 hour of complete rest, you instead become fatigued.</p>",
